name pdflscape
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Make landscape pages display as landscape
longdesc The package adds PDF support to the landscape environment of
longdesc package lscape, by setting the PDF /Rotate page attribute.
longdesc Pages with this attribute will be displayed in landscape
longdesc orientation by conforming PDF viewers.
